"title": "5323: gate",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5323: gate",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A point of entry to a walled city or walled-off area, such as the temple. It was a place where business was transacted and where justice and punishment were dispensed. It is used figuratively of the entry to death and also of the starting-point of the Christian life.</p>\n<h2>The purpose of gates as defended points of entry</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:5\">DEU 3:5</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:5\">JOS 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:7\">JOS 2:7</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg5:8\">JDG 5:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:7\">1SA 23:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr8:5\">2CH 8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr14:7\">2CH 14:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:16\">PSA 107:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:13\">PSA 147:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:7\">ISA 22:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:1-Isa45:2\">ISA 45:1–45:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:30\">JER 51:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:58\">JER 51:58</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek38:11\">EZK 38:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:9\">EZK 46:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:6\">HOS 11:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:12\">LUK 7:12</a> <em>Jesus Christ approaches Nain</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:24\">ACT 9:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:10\">ACT 12:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:13\">ACT 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:25\">REV 21:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:14\">REV 22:14</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of gates</h2>\n<h3>The gates of Jerusalem</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:13-Neh2:15\">NEH 2:13–2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs14:13\">2KI 14:13</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr25:23\">2CH 25:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:3\">NEH 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:3\">NEH 2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:8\">NEH 2:8</a>NEH <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:1\">3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:32\">NEH 3:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:2\">JHN 5:2</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:3\">NEH 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:6\">NEH 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:13-Neh3:15\">NEH 3:13–3:15</a> <em>the Valley Gate, Dung Gate and Fountain Gate</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:26\">NEH 3:26</a> <em>the Water Gate</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:28-Neh3:29\">NEH 3:28–3:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:31\">NEH 3:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:1\">NEH 6:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh7:3\">NEH 7:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh11:19\">NEH 11:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:39\">NEH 12:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps122:2\">PSA 122:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa60:11\">ISA 60:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:15\">JER 1:15</a></p>\n<h3>The gates of the temple</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:2\">ACT 3:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr23:19\">2CH 23:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:8\">2CH 24:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:2\">2CH 31:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:2\">JER 20:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:11\">EZK 44:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:10\">ACT 3:10</a></p>\n<h3>Other examples of gates</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:26\">JOS 6:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:17\">GEN 28:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:52\">1SA 17:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs16:34\">1KI 16:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:18\">MAT 16:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:1-John10:3\">JHN 10:1–10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:17\">ACT 10:17</a></p>\n<h2>Uses of the area around the gate</h2>\n<h3>A place of (sometimes false) worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:2\">2CH 31:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:8\">2KI 23:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:14\">PSA 9:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:19-Ps118:20\">PSA 118:19–118:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek46:2\">EZK 46:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:13\">ACT 14:13</a></p>\n<h3>A place of business</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:10-Gen23:11\">GEN 23:10–23:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:1\">RUT 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:11\">RUT 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:1\">2KI 7:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:18\">2KI 7:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:19-Neh13:22\">NEH 13:19–13:22</a></p>\n<h3>A place where decisions are made and justice dispensed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:19-Gen34:20\">GEN 34:19–34:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:19\">DEU 21:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:13-Deut22:19\">DEU 22:13–22:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:7-Deut25:10\">DEU 25:7–25:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh20:4\">JOS 20:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:2\">2SA 15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:10\">1KI 22:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:19\">EST 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:21\">EST 2:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth3:2-Esth3:3\">EST 3:2–3:3</a></p>\n<h3>A place of punishment, banishment and begging</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:5\">DEU 17:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:23-Deut22:24\">DEU 22:23–22:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:29\">JOS 8:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:3\">2KI 7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:2\">JER 20:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:15\">EZK 21:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:20\">LUK 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:12\">HEB 13:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:14-Rev22:15\">REV 22:14–22:15</a></p>\n<h3>A place of counsel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:20-Prov1:21\">PRO 1:20–1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:1-Prov8:3\">PRO 8:1–8:3</a></p>\n<h2>Figurative use of the gate</h2>\n<h3>Coming to worship</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:7-Ps24:10\">PSA 24:7–24:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:4\">PSA 100:4</a></p>\n<h3>The entrance to death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:10\">ISA 38:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job17:16\">JOB 17:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job38:17\">JOB 38:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:13\">PSA 9:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:18\">PSA 107:18</a></p>\n<h3>The entrance to the Christian life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:13-Matt7:14\">MAT 7:13–7:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:7-John10:10\">JHN 10:7–10:10</a></p>\n<h3>The entry to the heavenly city of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:14\">REV 22:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek48:30-Ezek48:34\">EZK 48:30–48:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:12-Rev21:15\">REV 21:12–21:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:21\">REV 21:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:25\">REV 21:25</a></p>",
